</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-96_"><b>Regular check-ins</b> - Conduct regular one-to-one meetings with employees to identify signs of burnout early and provide support.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-98_"><b>Promote an open culture</b> - Create a workplace culture where discussing mental health is as natural as discussing physical health.
